main event: An unidentified flying object was reported hovering over Parsippany, New Jersey, on November 6, 1967.
interesting points: The object appeared to be circular in shape and resembled a flying saucer,The sighting lasted for approximately 15 minutes,The object had a bright whitish glow with intermittent flashing lights around its perimeter,Multiple witnesses reported seeing the object at different times,Officer William Johnson took photographs of the object before it disappeared rapidly.
sighted object: a circular, glowing object resembling a flying saucer
witness description: Mrs. Jane Smith and an anonymous witness
